LaTeX key analysis variables

latex_key_analysis_vars.Rd

A data frame of key analysis variables in LaTeX formatting.

latex_key_analysis_vars

Format

A data frame with 2 columns.

var_name

The text name for key analysis variables.

latex_var_name

The LaTeX key analysis variable name.

Examples

latex_key_analysis_vars

#>          var_name   latex_var_name
#> 1  eta_engr_units          $\\eta$
#> 2             eta          $\\eta$
#> 3             p_s            $p_s$
#> 4         q_dot_s     $\\dot{q}_s$
#> 5         E_dot_s     $\\dot{E}_s$
#> 6       E_dot_emb $\\dot{E}_{emb}$
#> 7         C_dot_s     $\\dot{C}_s$
#> 8       C_dot_cap $\\dot{C}_{cap}$
#> 9        C_dot_md  $\\dot{C}_{md}$
#> 10        C_dot_o     $\\dot{C}_o$
#> 11          N_dot       $\\dot{N}$
#> 12          M_dot       $\\dot{M}$
